{"title":"红炉下乡","authors":["甘瑞"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红炉下乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘瑞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤响，响叮当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老刘围着红炉忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉前炉后成天累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水浸透裌衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整的挖锄明如镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装的铧犁排成行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"申队长，春耕忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开会半夜才回乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一见老刘忙不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢激动谈心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问声“老刘同志你不知累？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今年为啥这早就下乡！？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘师傅，申队长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相顾一笑意深长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进年代齐跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一早百早才像样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦思苦想闹革新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的秋后多收粮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}